This is IRC Master — a job management platform for building insurance repair businesses.

The full technical specification is in the file IRC_Master_Tech_Spec_v2_9.md in this project.
Read that file at the start of every session before doing anything else.

## Critical rules for every session:
- Read the spec before writing any code
- One session = one module only
- Deliver complete files only — no partial patches, no diffs
- Never modify files outside the current session's scope
- TypeScript throughout — no any types
- All database access through Supabase client only
- Every table has tenant_id — always filter by it
- Never expose SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY to the browser
- Follow the App Router structure exactly as defined in the spec (Section 7)
- Use shadcn/ui for all UI components
- Tailwind only for styling — black (#1a1a1a) and beige (#f5f0e8) palette
